name: Gallo the Hen
description: $GALLO is a Solana-based meme token born from the viral energy of TikTok star @ilgallinaio_special, who entertains millions with his hilarious chicken content. The project bridges real-world virality with on-chain culture, creating a fun and engaging entry point for new users. With plans to integrate sports partnerships, community rewards, and mass exposure through social media, $GALLO is more than a meme — it’s a movement to bring fresh eyes to Solana, powered by cluck-worthy content and cult-level engagement.
